{"tid":621454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士蘭桂坊外疑冚旗等客　外籍父子講價不成　涉打司機兼扑玻璃","createTime":"2018-04-08T10:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T14:47:52.000Z","uid":35964,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5839b3d90df8ef74313c72c1bf9b2698e8f00d11","tid":621454,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"凌晨2時許，一名57歲外籍男子MARK，帶同25歲兒子PAUL見識完蘭桂坊的魅力，走到中環威靈頓街與德己立街交界找的士離開，恰好一輛的士正在冚旗等客，父子兩人遂上前截車。然而，疑因「價錢不合」的問題，父子與的士司機發生爭執，期間39歲姓黎的士司機報警，稱被人毀壞的士及打傷。警方到場發現的士一扇玻璃窗碎裂，的士司機則面部有傷，經調查後以涉嫌「刑事毀壞」拘捕父親MARK，另以涉嫌「普通襲擊」拘捕兒子PAUL。案件交由中區警區刑事調查隊跟進，同時召救護車將司機送院。<br />\n<br />\n打得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26156e38f56ec73e9fcbab70fa71cfaef65a5133","tid":621454,"uid":77569,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:30:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5296d9d2bb9b89a2e5e0f92aa10bca03f007837b","tid":621454,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:31:39.000Z","msg":"的士狗死不足惜"},{"pid":"dae113bad725365a7406d5c0815da16a74af917d","tid":621454,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:32:23.000Z","msg":"啲廢中司機 又搞亂腥港"},{"pid":"04d9253254aec21c0ad5841ec5ea131c086620b7","tid":621454,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"班差佬咁都唔拉個的士司機 收幾倍價錢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82272ccdac006fe76a63fba0afebc7886df53b02","tid":621454,"uid":64564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街的士狗"},{"pid":"c6e6ae1a6b1b2e54b8cc93918f196042f3